	   <tr><td colspan=2>One of the best weapons to give to your pet is the relatively inexpensive gnoll hide lariat. The weapon drops from splitpaw gnolls, and can be bought relatively cheaply from players. The weapon processes a stun effect on the monsters. This is great for interrupting spells as well as keeping the damage the monster causes low as they can't hit when they are stunned.  :)<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
