	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hiyas,<br><br>  I found that in Rathe Mountains I could solo Clops, Cynthia and eventually Hill Giants by using Dark followed by Venom of snake and then Invoke fear.  Starting a HP to Mana drain b4 fight allows for vamp curse during fight.  If you time it right at about 10 seconds after venom of snake wears off so will dark.  So when you see venom of snake has worn off message reapply either dooming darkness or best ye got.  <br><br>  Send pet eithr b4 dark or after you fear depending on your style.  I would dark, poison and pull to safe spot then attack pet and fear. reapply dark afterpoison runs out and then med. variation would be to reapply venom to speed up kill.  When monster was just about dead I'd cast vamp curse and med as monster die.  Can regain about 1 bub HP with CoB and vamp curse running.<br><br>Good Hunting<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
